org.radeox.util.logging

Class Logger

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.radeox.util.logging.Logger

  • public class Logger
extends Object
    Logger for logging events. Logger uses al LoggerImplementation for logging concrete logging, e.g. SystemOutLogger
